        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Note 6: Manage secrets in different notebooks environments]]></title>
        <id>https://ivanignatiev.github.io/secrets-in-ds-notebooks</id>
        <link href="https://ivanignatiev.github.io/secrets-in-ds-notebooks"/>
        <updated>2025-03-29T09:30:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Look to tutorials for Data Engineers and Data Scientists, responses in Stackoverflow. Hardcoded credentials (CWE-798) are everywhere, if not in code, printed in output cell. Risk to push notebook with api-keys to git or a pipeline is very high.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Look to tutorials for Data Engineers and Data Scientists, responses in Stackoverflow. Hardcoded credentials (<a href="https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/798.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CWE-798</a>) are everywhere, if not in code, printed in output cell. Risk to push notebook with api-keys to git or a pipeline is very high.</p>
<p>Static analysis tools <code>pynblint</code> and <code>bandit</code> does not detect hardcoded secrets in notebooks. Issues can be caught during code review. However, file will be distributed across all team members PCs if merged in some shared branch.</p>
<p>Public services like GitHub and some serverless services (<a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/inspector/latest/user/scanning-lambda.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Scanning AWS Lambda functions with Amazon Inspector</a>) can identify <a href="https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/798.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CWE-798</a> but it does not reduce responsibilities of notebooks and code owners.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="local-notebooks">Local Notebooks<a href="https://ivanignatiev.github.io/secrets-in-ds-notebooks#local-notebooks" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Local Notebooks" title="Direct link to Local Notebooks">​</a></h2>
<p>Use environment variables, or <code>dotenv</code>, or <code>keyring</code>, or password inputs.</p>
<div class="language-python codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-python codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">secret_in_env </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> os</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">.</span><span class="token plain">environ</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'ENVIRONMENT_VARIABLE_WITH_SECRET_NAME'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p>Do not print your secret variables, or ensure your cell outputs are clean before committing to <code>git</code>.</p>
<p>If you store your secrets in <code>.env</code> file, add this file to <code>.gitignore</code>.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="google-colab-secrets">Google Colab Secrets<a href="https://ivanignatiev.github.io/secrets-in-ds-notebooks#google-colab-secrets" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Google Colab Secrets" title="Direct link to Google Colab Secrets">​</a></h2>
<div class="language-python codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-python codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">from</span><span class="token plain"> google</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">.</span><span class="token plain">colab </span><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">import</span><span class="token plain"> userdata</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">secret_in_env </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> userdata</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">.</span><span class="token plain">get</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'{googleColabSecretName}'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p>Figure. Google Colab Secrets:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" alt="Google Colab Secrets" src="https://ivanignatiev.github.io/assets/images/google-colab-secrets-287d7e8dcf22a10118a7dc1e79110a23.png" width="3840" height="1876" class="img_ev3q"></p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="databricks">Databricks<a href="https://ivanignatiev.github.io/secrets-in-ds-notebooks#databricks" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Databricks" title="Direct link to Databricks">​</a></h2>
<div class="language-python codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-python codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">username </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> dbutils</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">.</span><span class="token plain">secrets</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">.</span><span class="token plain">get</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token plain">scope </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">"{databricksSecretNamespace}"</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> key </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">"{databricksSecretName}"</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/databricks/security/secrets/example-secret-workflow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tutorial: Create and use a Databricks secret</a></p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="azure-devops">Azure DevOps<a href="https://ivanignatiev.github.io/secrets-in-ds-notebooks#azure-devops" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Azure DevOps" title="Direct link to Azure DevOps">​</a></h2>
<p>In MLOps, ModelOps in pipelines secrets can be stored over Variables Groups. Additionally, Variable Group can be linked to Azure KeyVault.</p>
<p>From Variables secrets can be populated as environment variables in pipelines.</p>
<p>Figure. Azure DevOps Variable Groups:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" alt="Azure DevOps Variable Groups" src="https://ivanignatiev.github.io/assets/images/azure-devops-variable-groups-d159801dc2815162886b3c2b42354a18.png" width="2540" height="1340" class="img_ev3q"></p>]]></content>
